__SqlaTable__.sql:
-- Note: Unless you save your query, these tabs will NOT persist if you clear your cookies or change browsers.

-- Note: Unless you save your query, these tabs will NOT persist if you clear your cookies or change browsers.

select
created_at,
last_updated_at,
get_json_object(p.process_data,'$.lmh_provider.v') as lmh_provider
from fareye_prod.process p
where p.company_id = 447
and p.process_master_id = 9279
and ((p.created_at_part) >= (to_date('{{from_dttm}}')) - interval 2 day)
and ((p.created_at_part) < (to_date('{{to_dttm}}')) + interval 1 day)
and get_json_object(p.process_data,'$.actual_pickup_date.v') is NOT NULL

-- Note: Unless you save your query, these tabs will NOT persist if you clear your cookies or change browsers.

WITH cte1 AS (
    SELECT
    reference_number,
    get_json_object(p.process_data,'$.destination_hub_code.v') as destination_hub_code,
    date_trunc('week', get_json_object(p.process_data,'$.actual_delivery_date.v')::DATE) as weekly_date,
    get_json_object(p.process_data,'$.actual_delivery_date.v')::DATE as delivered_date,
    get_json_object(p.process_data,'$.received_lmh_date.v')::DATE as receipt_date,
    CASE WHEN DAYOFWEEK(get_json_object(p.process_data,'$.actual_delivery_date.v')::DATE) IN (1, 7) THEN 0 ELSE 1 END AS delivered_weekday,
    CASE WHEN DAYOFWEEK(get_json_object(p.process_data,'$.received_lmh_date.v')::DATE) IN (1, 7) THEN 0 ELSE 1 END AS receipt_weekday,
    DATEDIFF(get_json_object(p.process_data,'$.received_lmh_date.v')::DATE, get_json_object(p.process_data,'$.actual_delivery_date.v')::DATE) AS total_days
    FROM fareye_prod.process p
    WHERE company_id= 447
    AND process_master_id = 9279
    and ((p.created_at_part) >= (to_date('{{from_dttm}}')) - interval 2 day)
    and ((p.created_at_part) < (to_date('{{to_dttm}}')) + interval 1 day)
    AND get_json_object(p.process_data,'$.actual_delivery_date.v') is NOT NULL
    AND get_json_object(p.process_data,'$.received_lmh_date.v') is NOT NULL 
),
cte2 AS (
    SELECT reference_number, delivered_date, receipt_date,
       CASE WHEN delivered_weekday = 0 OR receipt_weekday = 0 THEN 0
            ELSE CEILING(total_days - (total_days / 7) * 2 -
                 CASE WHEN DAYOFWEEK(receipt_date) < DAYOFWEEK(delivered_date) THEN 2 ELSE 0 END -
                 CASE WHEN DAYOFWEEK(receipt_date) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END +
                 CASE WHEN DAYOFWEEK(delivered_date) = 7 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)
       END AS business_days_difference
    FROM cte1
)

SELECT 
a.reference_number,
a.destination_hub_code,
a.weekly_date,
a.delivered_date,
a.receipt_date,
b.business_days_difference,
(case when b.business_days_difference > 2 THEN 1 ELSE  0 END ) as total_received_orders_oo_sla,
(case when b.business_days_difference > 5 THEN 1 ELSE  0 END ) as total_lah,
(case when b.business_days_difference > 5 AND a.destination_hub_code like 'X%' THEN 1 ELSE  0 END ) as total_lah_rxo,
(case when b.business_days_difference > 5 AND a.destination_hub_code like 'R%' THEN 1 ELSE  0 END ) as total_lah_ryder
FROM cte1 a
JOIN cte2 b
ON a.reference_number = b.reference_number

select

WITH cte1 AS (

    reference_number,
    get_json_object(p.process_data,'$.actual_delivery_date.v')::DATE as delivered_date,
    get_json_object(p.process_data,'$.received_lmh_date.v')::DATE as receipt_date,
    CASE WHEN DAYOFWEEK(get_json_object(p.process_data,'$.actual_delivery_date.v')::DATE) IN (1, 7) THEN 0 ELSE 1 END AS delivered_weekday,
    CASE WHEN DAYOFWEEK(get_json_object(p.process_data,'$.received_lmh_date.v')::DATE) IN (1, 7) THEN 0 ELSE 1 END AS receipt_weekday,
    DATEDIFF(get_json_object(p.process_data,'$.received_lmh_date.v')::DATE, get_json_object(p.process_data,'$.actual_delivery_date.v')::DATE) AS total_days
    FROM fareye_prod.process p
    WHERE company_id= 447
    AND process_master_id = 9279
    and ((p.created_at_part) >= (to_date('{{from_dttm}}')) - interval 2 day)
    and ((p.created_at_part) < (to_date('{{to_dttm}}')) + interval 1 day)
    AND get_json_object(p.process_data,'$.actual_delivery_date.v') is NOT NULL
    AND get_json_object(p.process_data,'$.received_lmh_date.v') is NOT NULL 
),
cte2 AS (
    SELECT reference_number, delivered_date, receipt_date,
       CASE WHEN delivered_weekday = 0 OR receipt_weekday = 0 THEN 0
            ELSE CEILING(total_days - (total_days / 7) * 2 -
                 CASE WHEN DAYOFWEEK(receipt_date) < DAYOFWEEK(delivered_date) THEN 2 ELSE 0 END -
                 CASE WHEN DAYOFWEEK(receipt_date) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END +
                 CASE WHEN DAYOFWEEK(delivered_date) = 7 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)
       END AS business_days_difference
    FROM cte1
)

b.business_days_difference,

(case when b.business_days_difference > 10 THEN 1 ELSE  0 END ) as 10_plus_days
FROM cte1 a
JOIN cte2 b
ON a.reference_number = b.reference_number
